name: Murmurs of Byte Streams #06
description:
I always have a lot of imagination about what information looks like on the Internet.
All kinds of information are created by all kinds of people all over the world, with the emotional tones of people's joys and sorrows, with the objective fragments of the topic, with different languages, cultures, and tones.
They intersect over high-speed, rough channels. They infest each other in the wide, crowded void.
What strange images will those bits, bytes, and streams form in such a global carnival of humanity?
Murmurs of Byte Streams is my personal expression of these scenes.
